Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:47.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She came, demanding tribute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our harvest hers to consume
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As our hunger continued
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:01.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It seemed she'd be our doom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:06.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There was no one to stop her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:11.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This Sphinx a beast so daunting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:16.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yet still our Prince would be stirred
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To resist her taunting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The beast was displeased
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:30.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Snatched him away to her temple lair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For him to be freed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:39.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her riddle must be solved if we dare
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we owe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:49.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All that shines as the Glowpaz glows
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from faith
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:57.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from Hope~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:08.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew it was my doing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:13.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From such an innocent alm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:18.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Quickly I galloped after
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew I must save Hi~san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She asked me the phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:32.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One simple riddle with all at stake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then, I would elate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:42.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew the answer without mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The sphinx scrunched up her wicked face
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To hear the answer found
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She roared and said "you'll know your place"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then stomped against the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But the riddles' solved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"You're not absolved"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She said with leering eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"Your bounty still belongs to me"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her word, a hollow lie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could not leave the Prince in chains
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And let her steal from everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But what about another game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A challenge all or none"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But if I win you'll go away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And leave our village be"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Sphinx intrigued said: "We shall see"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then laughed aloud in glee
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Blind and without wings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:20.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She had me cross that most dangerous pool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I made the leap
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:30.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I held to Hope like a precious jewel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we owe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All that shines as the Glowpaz glows
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from faith
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I was blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I still owe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:54.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could tell you "no"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I will come
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:01.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Bring them Hope~!